cks\ncatalogues created for the Baryon Oscillation Spectroscopic Survey (BOSS) Date\nRelease 11 samples covering 0.43 < z < 0.7 (CMASS) and 0.15 < z < 0.43 (LOWZ),\nto empirically test these changes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 6 Aug 2014 16:36:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 25 Feb 2015 09:53:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-02-26"}
