inuum, which is\nconsistent with the simple reprocessing scenario. The variability level of CTS\nC30.10 and the measurement accuracy of the line and continuum is high enough to\nexpect that further monitoring will allow to measure the time delay between the\nMg II line and continuum.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 7 Aug 2014 09:22:04 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 8 Aug 2014 17:12:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-10-15"}
